-- U.K. Stocks Erase Earlier Losses; Rio Tinto, BHP Billiton Reverse Decline
-- Adam Haigh
-- 2010-06-23T12:17:38Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-23/u-k-stocks-erase-earlier-losses-rio-tinto-bhp-billiton-reverse-decline.html

          
          
             U.K. stocks erased their losses,
with the benchmark FTSE 100 Index little changed at 5,245.23 as
of 1:15 p.m. in London.  
 Rio Tinto Group and BHP Billiton Ltd. reversed earlier
declines, rising 0.8 percent to 3,473.5 pence and 0.6 percent to
2,000 pence, respectively.  
          
          


  


        